{"tid":2416533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（武漢肺炎）德科學家稱「病毒99.9%來自實驗室」 　中使館強烈不滿：是天災","createTime":"2021-02-21T06:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T12:56:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"187d7e6c9c90e4b0578cc72da59a555b611a774e","tid":2416533,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:48:57.000Z","msg":"中國駐外大使館近日頻頻發言反駁外媒對武肺炎的報導。繼中國駐法國大使館駁斥武漢中心醫院眼科醫生李文亮並非「吹哨者」，「吃人血饅頭」後，駐德國大使館今（2/21）發聲明，反駁德國漢堡大學（Universit&auml;t Hamburg）的物理學者維森丹格（Roland Wiesendanger），稱「病毒99.9%來自實驗室」的說法，批評刊登訪問的德國《畫報》（Bild）「散佈和炒作病毒源自武漢實驗室洩露的陰謀論」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210221/STLRD6RL3RD5NEVNBQCNYVNSVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210221%2FSTLRD6RL3RD5NEVNBQCNYVNSVU%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=c82b2191\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210221%2FSTLRD6RL3RD5NEVNBQCNYVNSVU%2F&h=6c3297dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210221/STLRD6RL3RD5NEVNBQCNYVNSVU/</a>"},{"pid":"72dfc7957a04f893c11fa63f12866d8ce2745a8a","tid":2416533,"uid":47081,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"是天災！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n責任不在中方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f39e0bf656e205c88ffe432b66140ce6480bc31","tid":2416533,"uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"責任全在天方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c928b6aece0f163be9a1eb08c23d97f48d62d8","tid":2416533,"uid":28770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"又話源頭係意大利，點解中國領事館要強烈不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" clas